      "name": "createServer([requestListener])",
      "kind": "function",
      "status": "supported",
      "notes": "Creates an HTTP server whose request listener receives IncomingMessage and ServerResponse objects. Requests are parsed as HTTP/1.1 over node:net, request bodies stream incrementally, and unsupported CONNECT/upgrade/Expect requests are rejected explicitly rather than partially emulated.",
